git topics setup
  hooks
    prevent untagged master pushes
    prevent non-merge develop pushes

git topics reintegrate
  git checkout next
  git reset --hard master
  git merge every previously integrated topic
    like git rebase -i, just select which topics you want to reintegrate
  --onto <branch>
    for experimental uses like `git topics reintegrate --onto throwaway`
  --continue | --skip | --abort | --quit | --edit-todo
    like the counterparts in git rebase

